</p><note>
<p>
<b>structured_text_content</b> would only not be provided if there was no need to specify lower level markup within the current 
markup or if <b>plain_text_content</b> were provided.
</p>
</note>
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_arm.Structured_text.precedent_structured_text"><p>
specifies the role of the <b>Structured_text</b> for the <b>Structured_text</b>.  
