<p>
<b>precedent_structured_text</b> is provided to ensure the correct sequencing of text contents.
</p>
</note>
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_arm.Structured_text.plain_text_content"><p>
specifies the role of the <express_ref linkend="Characteristic:arm:Characteristic_arm.Text_representation_item"/> for the <b>Structured_text</b>. The <b>plain_text_content</b> need not be provided for the <b>Structured_text</b>. The value of this attribute need not be specified. 
</p><note>
<p>
<b>plain_text_content</b> would only not be provided if there was a need to specify lower level markup within the current markup.
</p>
</note>
</ext_description>
